description: Dudes and dudettes of Denton are undoubtedly delighted and dazzled by the all the delicious frozen desserts that you find at Kona Ice!This festive truck is bringing flavor and fun to everyone; adults, kids, and of course UNT students, all dive right into these divinely sweet icy treats. Flavor your day or your next part-tay the delectable way with Kona Ice of Denton.
name: Kona Ice of Denton
